# Automata Logger
Default logger is set to log to STDOUT.

## Packaging
`python3 -m build`

## Usage
1. `ConfigureLogger()`
2. `logging.info('test')` or `logging.getLogger('--REF-NAME--)`

## Development
1. Get into `venv`
2. `pip install .` (should hook into setuptools)
